************************************
*****
*****  PHP SCRIPTING LANGUAGE  *****
*****
************************************


PHP is a web server based scripting programming language.

For those using Linux, there is a script named "setup-php-linux.sh" which will
download various PHP Scripting language related documentation to your computer.
It will require Subversion (SVN), Git and Hg (Mercurial) to be installed.


Links:

http://php.net/
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Php


Books:

ISBN-13: 9781449392772 -- PROGRAMMING PHP
ISBN-13: 9780596101015 -- PHP COOKBOOK (2nd Edition)
ISBN-13: 9781494267353 -- THE JOY OF PHP

